Usage: set_pulse_clock_max_width [-help] <pulse_width> <object_list>
                                 [-transitive_fanout]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<pulse_width>          # Pulse width value (float, required)
<object_list>          # List of objects: pulse generator cells, pulse
                       # generator library cells, clocks or current_design
                       # (string, required)
-transitive_fanout     # Pulse width value for transitive fanout
                       # (bool, optional)